  <h3>Changing the button text</h3>
  <p>You can change the text on the button and in the "No file chosen" message. This text is changeable so you can translate it or be specific about the file to upload.</p>
  <p>Keep the text as short as possible. Screen reader users, for example, might find it difficult to use the component if the text is too long.</p>
  <p>All the text in the component can be translated to match the language of the page content when JavaScript is running.</p>

  <h3>Error messages</h3>
  <p>Style error messages like this.</p>

  {{ designExample({
